# AnyPOD4Me — Marketing-Polished Build

- Landing hero with clear CTAs, promo banner, examples, pricing
- DTG-only tees, square 4500×4500 upscale, no-words prompts, optional text overlay
- 3-free images → Stripe Checkout
- Google Analytics + Meta Pixel (env-driven)

## Setup
1) Copy `.env.example` → `.env` and fill keys.
2) `npm install`
3) `npm start`
4) Visit http://localhost:3000

## Deploy (Render)
- Build: `npm install`
- Start: `node server.js`
- Add env vars → Deploy
